'''BG集團'''（BG Group plc）是一家總部位於英國[[伯克郡|伯克郡]][[雷丁|雷丁]]的跨國能源公司<ref>"[http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Pages/pgContactUs.aspx General contacts] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Pages/pgContactUs.aspx |date=20101021072039 }}." BG Group. Retrieved on 5 November 2010. "Address: BG Group plc Thames Valley Park, Reading, Berkshire, RG6 1PT United Kingdom"</ref><ref>"[http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Pages/pgDirectionstoBGReading.aspx Directions to BG Reading] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Pages/pgDirectionstoBGReading.aspx |date=20101005014851 }}." BG Group. Retrieved on 5 November 2010. [http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Documents/BG_Map_TVP_May09.pdf PDF Map] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bg-group.com/ContactUs/Documents/BG_Map_TVP_May09.pdf |date=20101222095553 }}.</ref>。它運營於各大洲總共25個國家，每日平均開採680,000[[桶油當量|BOE]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bg-group.com/AboutBG/Pages/BGProfile.aspx|title=BG Group Profile|accessdate=24 August 2010|publisher=BG Group plc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100817050645/http://www.bg-group.com/AboutBG/Pages/BGProfile.aspx|archivedate=2010年8月17日|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bg-group.com/InvestorRelations/Results/Documents/2010/BG_Q2_2010.pdf|title=2010 Second Quarter & Half Year Results|accessdate=31 August 2010|publisher=BG Group plc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101221173006/http://www.bg-group.com/InvestorRelations/Results/Documents/2010/BG_Q2_2010.pdf|archive-date=2010-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。它也是美國最大的[[液化天然氣|液化天然氣]]供應商<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bg-group.com/OurBusiness/OurBusiness/Pages/LNG.aspx|title=Liquefied Natural Gas – an enabling technology|accessdate=31 August 2010|publisher=BG Group plc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100607041706/http://www.bg-group.com/OurBusiness/OurBusiness/Pages/LNG.aspx|archive-date=2010-06-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

BG集團曾在[[倫敦證券交易所|倫敦證券交易所]]上市，也曾是[[富時100指數|富時100指數]]成分。{{as of|2012|7|6}}，該公司市值為449億英鎊，是當時倫敦證券交易所全部上市公司中的第七大公司。<ref>{{Cite web| url=http://www.stockchallenge.co.uk/ftse.php| title=FTSE All-Share Index Ranking| publisher=stockchallenge.co.uk| accessdate=26 December 2011| archive-date=2012-03-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310231136/http://www.stockchallenge.co.uk/ftse.php| dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年4月8日[[荷蘭皇家殼牌|荷蘭皇家殼牌]]與BG集團達成協議；以470億英鎊收購BG集團股份。這是業界自1996年以來第四大收購，亦是截至2015年來最大，新公司將會成为全球最大液化天然氣生產商。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cn.nytimes.com/global-biz/20150409/c09shell/zh-hant/ |title=殼牌擬以700億美元收購BG集團- 纽约时报中文网 |accessdate=2015-05-17 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518105417/http://cn.nytimes.com/global-biz/20150409/c09shell/zh-hant/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2016年2月15日，BG集團在[[倫敦證券交易所|倫敦證券交易所]]除牌<REF>
